  <h2>Esquimalt Graving Dock Booking Application</h2>

  <p>
    The booking application is used by clients of the dockyard to reserve
    times and spaces for their vessels.  Once a booking is requested an email
    gets sent to the administrators at the dock who then login, manage the
    bookings and confirm or deny the requests based on the overall scheduling
    concerns of the dock.
  </p>
